					2072 Chaitra
1)WAP to check whether a no is triangular no or not.

2)WAP to calculate sum of digits of a given 5-digits no entered by the user using recursive function.

3)WAP to read 3*3 matrix and find the minimum integer. Replace the diagonal element by the minimum element and display it using pointer.

4)WAP to read structure 'college' having name, estDate and location where estDate is an another structure having day, month and year as member. Display the records of 10 colleges.

5)WAP to read information of a file named 'data.txt' and write its contents to another file 'record.txt'.